   <title>Examples of Basic Operations</title>
   <para>
      You can interact with this API using the programming language of your choice.
      The examples we show here demonstrate how to work with this API in a few popular languages.
      For other languages, you may be able to adapt the examples in  
      <link xlink:href="http://developer.rackspace.com/#home-sdks">Rackspace Software Development Kits</link>, 
      showing how to work with other Rackspace REST APIs. 
   </para>
